{"tid":2133093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又翻译了一首香港革命战歌为国语","createTime":"2020-07-30T23:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T12:27:36.000Z","uid":334191,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d42dfcff7fe5d3df17a131817516d51c303838","tid":2133093,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T23:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbbvfLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbbvfLH.jpg&h=83d72809&s={SIZE}\" /> 可惜我自己唱不好，会唱原版，一唱翻译版就走调了，不然一定发墙内。<br />\n东突厥斯坦国歌国语墙内版：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Y5411a7KR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2FBV1Y5411a7KR&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG15uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=e6d461f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Y5411a7KR</a><br />\n六四歌曲《天安门》墙内版： <a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1wC4y187Rz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2FBV1wC4y187Rz&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG15uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=fd9fa5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1wC4y187Rz</a><br />\n后一首歌曲是别人谱曲、我写词，为了对付审查，中文的词和国语的词有出入（含沙射影 VS 直接唱坦克要烧红旗）。"},{"pid":"767276dfff25aeda7348f7e030196ebe1eb7c0d5","tid":2133093,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T23:14:40.000Z","msg":"殘轉繁都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b9c13c0d125fddd44fd094ae8d2dda7267787f","tid":2133093,"uid":212731,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T23:22:50.000Z","msg":"post上bilibili<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持你 加油"},{"pid":"bf2eb2